ll town called <strong>Canela Town</strong>. Something perverse has the whole town in its grip...<br></li><li>Part 2: After the tragedy of Canela Town, <strong>Laurel Town</strong> - a nearby place - prepares for its summer festival, unaware that what happened to Canela Town could happen to them.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442060/extras/6729eef947655e028ae96d1e21ee1cf2.poster.avif?t=1720842927\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442060/extras/6729eef947655e028ae96d1e21ee1cf2.webm?t=1720842927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442060/extras/6729eef947655e028ae96d1e21ee1cf2.mp4?t=1720842927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A lot of Channels to watch<br></li><li>Rotoscope Animations<br></li><li>Smaller sized minigames in special channels<br></li><li>2 compilations of small horror stories<br></li><li>Unknown channels with weird happenings<br></li><li>And a lot of static...</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442060/extras/3aa331138d595e7e017da36c173c650d.poster.avif?t=1720842927\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442060/extras/3aa331138d595e7e017da36c173c650d.webm?t=1720842927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442060/extras/3aa331138d595e7e017da36c173c650d.mp4?t=1720842927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
